text: Jaime Ryan (born 8 May 1994) is an Australian competitive sailor. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the women's 470 class. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Australia Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 470
